WEBVTT

49:05.900 --> 49:08.442
This is the connection
between all these murders.

49:11.025 --> 49:12.984
I thought you will not find it ever.

49:13.275 --> 49:14.442
Good that you have found it.

49:15.025 --> 49:16.234
I don't need your approval.

49:16.900 --> 49:18.775
Now that I know the
reason behind your killings.

49:18.859 --> 49:21.775
How did you kill them?
Which weapon did you use?

49:21.859 --> 49:22.359
Tell me.

49:22.984 --> 49:24.525
For me to tell that...

49:25.317 --> 49:26.192
there is a condition.

49:26.359 --> 49:28.109
How many more conditions will you have?

49:28.484 --> 49:29.609
This is the last.

49:30.734 --> 49:31.609
Say it out.
